<div id="block-53d78e54-be46-414c-a3e1-7ffe9612eb4b" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="53d78e54-be46-414c-a3e1-7ffe9612eb4b" data-type="core/paragraph" aria-label="Block: Paragraph">
<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">Itâ€™s just like when you ask your partner: â€œWho is the best band on planet Earth?â€ and they instantly answer â€œImagine Dragonsâ€. You feel a chill going down your spine, and your eyes widen in admiration, and your heartbeats start to race, and you feel like saying just one word: â€œI love you!â€</p>
</div>
<div id="block-37d41b20-8d1f-4617-894d-9ca9d38839ab" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="37d41b20-8d1f-4617-894d-9ca9d38839ab" data-type="core/paragraph" aria-label="Block: Paragraph">
<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">A good Client-Agency relationship is the very base of success. <a href="https://www.petrikorsolutions.com/2019/09/03/social-media-marketing-agency-services/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Marketing agencies (opens in a new tab)">Marketing agencies</a> talk in the voice of clients to communicate to their audience, thus directly affecting the sales. Thatâ€™s why both parties should be on the same page.</p>
</div>
<div id="block-5dc29e60-3d34-4440-8048-86461efd9d15" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="5dc29e60-3d34-4440-8048-86461efd9d15" data-type="core/paragraph" aria-label="Block: Paragraph">
<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">Like any relationship, when peace and tranquility dominate the atmosphere, it creates the perfect environment for creativity to bloom and thrive. This calmness leads to immense productivity that inevitably results in a positive outcome. When the client and the agency are in sync, both can contribute to producing creative projects that are most likely to smash the ground. Therefore, increase sales and generate more revenues. Itâ€™s a win-win situation.</p>
</div>
<div id="block-6d7425fb-1dc5-459b-a2e7-27f144ec3d51" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="6d7425fb-1dc5-459b-a2e7-27f144ec3d51" data-type="core/paragraph" aria-label="Block: Paragraph">
<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">Being the <strong><em>boutique agency</em></strong> that held digital marketing for <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Noir.e.Blanc.chocolatier/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Noir Ã© Blanc (opens in a new tab)">Noir Ã© Blanc</a>, and due to the success of these marketing campaigns, many other clients reached us to help them in their social media marketing. Consequently, the agency could then â€œCross Collaborateâ€ to create one hell of a content starring all of our beloved brands.</p>
</div>
<div id="block-fe7c31eb-e8ef-42ac-9e8a-51bc4f901fa3" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="fe7c31eb-e8ef-42ac-9e8a-51bc4f901fa3" data-type="core/heading" aria-label="Block: Heading">
<h3 class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Write headingâ€¦">Trust is key!</h3>
</div>
<div id="block-175bd565-0695-497d-9b58-648e193ecffb" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="175bd565-0695-497d-9b58-648e193ecffb" data-type="core/paragraph" aria-label="Block: Paragraph">
<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">Also, trust is an important factor in any relationship. Marketing agencies are more updated in <a href="https://www.petrikorsolutions.com/2018/04/11/digital-marketing-trends-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="marketing trends (opens in a new tab)">marketing trends</a>, technology, SEO tools. So, clients need to trust agencies that they can capture the largest number of audience thus keeping them positively busy. At this point, the <strong><em>boutique agency</em></strong> creates wonderful content that satisfies the client and in return, the client assures the agency and provides it with a sense of security.</p>
</div>
<div id="block-f023b7ed-12e2-460c-b6c3-748d29fa2b6e" class="wp-block block-editor-block-list__block has-selected-ui" tabindex="0" role="group" data-block="f023b7ed-12e2-460c-b6c3-748d29fa2b6e" data-type="core/paragraph" aria-label="Block: Paragraph">
<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">Moreover, teamwork and â€œfriendshipâ€ is what makes or breaks a relationship. I like to think of this phase as the â€œGolden Eraâ€ in the relationship, especially when those two elements are available. I think this is the appropriate time to come out to the public and announce that youâ€™re â€œIn a Relationshipâ€. It is the perfect time to meet the other partner's friends and family, and once again emphasizing the importance of "Cross Collaborations."</p>
</div>
